template: SELECT MIN(movie_info_idx.note) AS movie_info_idx_note, MIN(info_type.id) AS info_type_id, MIN(name.id) AS name_id FROM movie_info_idx, name, complete_cast, info_type, title, cast_info WHERE info_type.id = movie_info_idx.info_type_id AND cast_info.person_id = name.id AND cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND complete_cast.movie_id = title.id AND movie_info_idx.movie_id = title.id AND title.production_year > %s AND name.name_pcode_cf BETWEEN 'A' AND 'F' AND name.gender = %s AND name.name NOT LIKE %s AND title.episode_nr > %s AND name.name LIKE %s AND info_type.info = %s;
